OL,4,CRefund plan for energy bills when
OL,5,Cdirect debits are too high
OL,6, Customers who pay too much to their
OL,7, energy supplier through their monthly
OL,8, direct debit payment should receive
OL,9, automatic annual refunds, Ofgem says.
OL,11,FFor years, customers have complained
OL,12,Fthat energy firms can hoard thousands
OL,13,Fof pounds of overpayments and would
OL,14,Fonly return it on request.
OL,16,FNow the regulator has proposed balances
OL,17,Fare cleared once a year, claiming
OL,18,Fsuppliers held a surplus of #1.4bn.
OL,20,FIt said some were using the money for
OL,21,F"unsustainable business practices".
